The Heimdall Application Dashboard plugin has been installed
- The plugin works out-of-the box with the default settings
- By default, the interface listens on both ports 80 and 443
- The SSL certificate is located in /usr/local/share/certs/
- The default Nginx config file is copied from /usr/local/etc/heimdall/nginx-heimdall-default.conf

Plugin option:
- To use HTTPS only, activate the HTTPSREDIRECT option as follows:
    
    iocage set -P httpsredirect=true heimdall-jailname

